Package model

Class QuestionsAndAnswersData

java.lang.Object
model.QuestionsAndAnswersData
public class QuestionsAndAnswersData extends Object
This class is used to store all the answers and questions from the current test. It also sends the data to a tests_data-txt file. Uses 2 array lists to store the data. One for the answers and one for the questions.
